                            <a href="http://www.mri.cnrs.fr/">
                                Montpellier RIO Imaging
                            </a>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="description">National Center for Scientific Research Montpellier</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 item">
